title: United Kingdom Imports of Oil
description: Imports of Oil in the United Kingdom decreased to 5178 GBP Million in September from 5851 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Oil in the United Kingdom averaged 1341.16 GBP Million from 1970 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 6172 GBP Million in June of 2022 and a record low of 49 GBP Million in March of 1970. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Oil.
author: Office For National Statistics, U.k.
